{"text_id":138848,"tokens":["In"," distributed"," sensing",","," the"," amount"," of"," data"," generated"," is"," often"," proportional"," to"," the"," size"," of"," the"," region"," being"," sensed","."," One"," approach"," to"," scale"," sensing"," efforts"," is"," to"," partition"," the"," region"," into"," smaller"," segments",","," each"," with"," a"," small"," field"," of"," view"," (","FOV",")."," In"," this"," approach",","," computation"," is"," performed"," locally"," at"," each"," sensing"," node"," and"," data"," aggregation"," is"," only"," needed"," within"," a"," segment","."," Compared"," with"," the"," traditional"," approach"," that"," requires"," all"," sensing"," nodes"," to"," communicate"," with"," a"," fusion"," center",","," the"," estimation"," diversity"," and"," energy"," efficiency"," can"," be"," significantly"," improved"," by"," leveraging"," local"," computation"," at"," each"," node","."," However",","," it"," is"," not"," clear"," how"," to"," perform"," distributed"," optimization"," for"," parameter"," estimation"," without"," any"," global"," communication",","," which"," could"," potentially"," consume"," significant"," energy","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," propose"," a"," novel"," distributed"," algorithm"," that"," performs"," estimation"," by"," locally"," computing"," the"," gradient"," of"," the"," cost"," function"," at"," each"," node"," and"," by"," efficiently"," communicating"," a"," small"," amount"," of"," information"," among"," neighboring"," nodes","."," Numerical"," results"," show"," that"," the"," proposed"," algorithm"," can"," achieve"," similar"," estimation"," accuracy"," as"," the"," centralized"," algorithm"," while"," reducing"," energy"," consumption"," by"," ","6","0","%"," for"," a"," network"," of"," nodes"," with"," homogeneous"," computation"," and"," communication"," capabilities",".'"," The"," rest"," of"," the"," paper"," is"," organized"," as"," follows","."," Section"," II"," presents"," related"," work","."," Section"," III"," describes"," the"," network"," model"," and"," problem"," statement","."," Section"," IV"," presents"," the"," gradient"," computation"," and"," communication"," based"," algorithm","."," Section"," V"," presents"," the"," numerical"," results","."," Finally",","," Section"," VI"," concludes"," the"," paper","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"dolly","label":1}